- Use tools/extract ONE AT A TIME.
- INPUT FORMAT EXACTLY: oz#chats/260322 | Extract bookmarks with [ ] or [-] and a blurb of key themes.
- Do not re-process files you've already extracted.

PHASE 3 - COMPILATION:
- When all files are extracted, compile the observations into a single Markdown document.
- Write to oz#archive/devlog/review-260330 using tools/write
- Format INPUT as:["oz#archive/devlog/review-260330", "# Sprint Review\n\n..."]

PHASE 4 - CONFIRM:
- Output <<ANSWER>> with save location and summary

RULES:
- Check AGENT STATE before each action
